Program: Omnibus
Title: The Peace Walkers
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p0376m9f
Last Broadcast Date: 30 October 2001
Inspired by anti-nuclear protests in London, two young Indians, Satish Kumar and E P Menon set off on an 8000 mile peace walk from India to the four capitals of the nuclear world. Here they recall their journey.